_:N9a990ddbd70849a5a82d4505221eaec4 <http://schema.org/description> "<p>Tim Bestwick was appointed UKAEA’s Interim Chief Executive Officer in July 2025.</p>\n\n<p>Career highlights include:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>Chief Development Officer and Deputy CEO, UKAEA</li>\n  <li>Chief Technology Officer and Director of Strategy, Communications &amp; Business Development, UKAEA</li>\n  <li>Executive Director, Business &amp; Innovation at the Science &amp; Technology Facilities Council.</li>\n  <li>Non-Executive Director of the Harwell Science &amp; Innovation Campus.</li>\n  <li>Chair of the Eureka Network (the world’s largest international business to business innovation network).</li>\n  <li>Non-Executive Director of ten start-up technology companies.</li>\n  <li>‘Innovation Sector Champion’ Award from AIRTO - the membership body for organisations operating in the UK’s innovation, research and technology sector.</li>\n  <li>Chair of The Space Partnership Board</li>\n</ul>\n" <https://forgetmenot.local/extractor/jsonld> .
